{"tid":1288992,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中嚴重刺激樓價飛升","createTime":"2019-07-06T01:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:00:48.000Z","uid":166667,"like":15,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6e02cbd5d408169357c716809daa53aa681dc9e7","tid":1288992,"uid":166667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"1. 反送中二百萬零一人出街，林鄭嚇到失禁，<span style=\"color: green;\">填海計劃</span>胎死腹中，相信未來幾年不會再提。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 立法會衝擊事件，<span style=\"color: red;\">空置稅</span>同樣胎死腹中，今年唔會再卡立法會，出年也是排到無期，唔夠膽再上立法會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 公私營<span style=\"color: purple;\">合作發展農地</span>，因為驚被指官商勾結，同樣胎死腹中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 林鄭樣樣唔夠膽做，目前唯一可做，等<span style=\"color: maroon;\">樓價瘋狂再升五成</span>，等全城焦點轉移去樓價，然後到時再出手調整，重提填海空置稅以凝聚民意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，目前樓價上望升五成完全無阻力，配合減息潮，升災會好得人驚！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28342686&amp;extra=&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28342686%26extra%3D%26page%3D1&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=cae9ce5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28342686&amp;extra=&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"2da72635d6061cef0e639127e839ef1fa48290cb","tid":1288992,"uid":257736,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijXNMgW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijXNMgW.jpg&h=f175fc70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f13f6b5b78892ebe85847bb96e5335f313b10997","tid":1288992,"uid":166667,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e02cbd5d408169357c716809daa53aa681dc9e7","tid":1288992,"uid":166667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"1. 反送中二百萬零一人出街，林鄭嚇到失禁，<span style=\"color: green;\">填海計劃</span>胎死腹中，相信未來幾年不會再提。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 立法會衝擊事件，<span style=\"color: r